            "id": 6008267,
            "title": "投信、自營商反手出貨 三大法人賣超65.04億元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (5) 日早盤開高，一度上漲 120 點，但隨著逼近前高套牢區間，加上追價意願有限，終場僅小漲 56.34 點，收在 21764.43 點，持續往半年線靠攏，成交量 3587 億元；三大法人合計賣超 65.04 億元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008267%2Fl%2Fe1c2765a0b0f90d455457d82c9382c81.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">投信、自營商反手出貨 三大法人賣超65.04億元。(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察三大法人今天籌碼動向，外資買超 0.66 億元；自營商賣超 40.17 億元；投信賣超 25.53 億元，終止連 12 買；三大法人合計賣超 65.04 元。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
