        {
            "id": 6007760,
            "title": "李在明提名的新總理 曾在哈佛、清華留學",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>韓國總統李在明周三（4 日）在龍山總統府公布新內閣首批人選，共同民主黨最高委員金民錫被提名為國務總理。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007760%2Fl%2F467f7274b8ac0881ceebfd085fa65919.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">韓國總統李在明周三在龍山總統府公布新內閣首批人選。（圖：Shutterstock）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據《韓聯社》周三報導，李在明表示，新政府將以忠誠、責任和實幹作為用人標準，開啟國民主權政府的新篇章。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>他提到金民錫時說，金民錫是四屆國會議員，現任民主黨首席最高委員，具備對國家治理的深刻洞察力和政策執行力，兼具細致務實與整合政治能力，是帶領國家克服危機、恢復民生經濟的合適人選。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金民錫在 1991 年步入政壇，1996 年當選第 15 屆國會議員後成功連任，2020 年當選第 21 屆國會議員之後連任兩屆。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金民錫畢業於首爾大學社會學系，獲美國哈佛大學肯尼迪政治學院行政學系碩士學位，並在中國清華大學法學院獲法學碩士學位。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
